The paper discusses the perspective we take on a system and how it influences the features and properties we focus on, the causes we search for, and the formalism we use to convey information. This suggests a focus on systems and their interactions, which could fall under the categories of social and information networks (cs.SI), systems and control (cs.SY), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and machine learning (cs.LG).
